Squirtle (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0006: Charizard
Pokémon
#0008: Wartortle →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Squirtle (TCG Pocket).

Squirtle has been featured on 26 different cards since it debuted in the Base Set of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Squirtle cards are normally Water-type Basic Pokémon.

Squirtle
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
